snippet.title: Greyseth
snippet.description:
I mainly create videos about Ben 10 and gaming. I make stuff like comparisons, reviews, theories, etc.
Sometimes I also upload meme videos, if I really have no idea what to upload.

The delay between videos should be about 3-5 days. or more if the video is long.

I also make games btw.
